channel.description:
Hello and welcome to FurkanScape V3 Dev Team
Server Features: Working Specials Working Mini-Games Working Skills Working killing monsters to level up
Server UPDATES: Making SafeZones Fully Working NPC drops Changing Item Bonuses
[center]Owners/Co-Owners -Mod Furkan -ItzKyle -[/center]
[center]Administrators -Own3d for 3v3r FULL[/center]
[center]Mods - -[/center]
[center]Forum Admins - -[/center]
[center]Coders -Syrillia -DuhPk[/center]
If you are applying for coders you must know about everything on the server updates. If you are appling for administrators you must know when you know and not know when to ban players or ip them. If you are applying for moderators you must know when to kick them and when not to. When you are applying for forum Administrators or Moderators you must know when to lock or sticky topics.
Use this format to apply.
[code]Name: In-Game Name: Msn: How often will you be on: Proof: Intelligence:[/code]
You must have MSN You must join Forums.
Thankz for reading.
~~~Furkan~~~
